      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Will cut off him that is shut up — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Those who had escaped the fury of their enemies invading them, either because they were ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "shut up ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "in caves, or castles, or strong towns: or, because they were ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "left, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "overlooked, or neglected by them, or spared as poor, impotent, helpless creatures. But now, saith he, they shall be all searched out, and brought to destruction. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "As a man taketh away dung — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Which they remove as a loathsome thing, out of their houses, and that thoroughly and universally. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Shall the fowls of the air eat — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So both sorts shall die and lie on the ground unburied.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
